('Clínica Dental Bonadex', 'Dental', 'English-speaking dental clinic in Barcelona located on Passeig de la Bonanova in the Sarrià-Sant Gervasi district. Founded 25 years ago by Dr. Pere Harster and Dr. Lopez Roura, Bonadex is a reference clinic in Spain specializing in prosthesis and oral rehabilitation, dental esthetics, and endodontics. The clinic offers comprehensive dental care with all specialties under one roof for personalized and individualized treatment. Services include dental implants, prosthodontics (crowns, bridges, dentures), dental esthetics, endodontics (root canals), conservative dentistry, orthodontics, periodontal disease treatment, pediatric dentistry, neurofocal dentistry, oral dysfunctions treatment, and snoring and sleep apnea solutions. The professional team is led by Dra. Dolores Rodríguez with highly qualified staff in constant training and active participation in scientific societies. The clinic philosophy focuses on preserving natural dentition through prevention and achieving excellence in all treatments. Full English-speaking staff with English website available.', 'Passeig de la Bonanova, 69, 3º', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 934 184 433', 'secretaria@bonadex.com', 'https://clinica-dental-bonadex.com/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
